             was indicted for <rs id="t18080217-54-off314" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18080217-54-off314" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080217-54-off314" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18080217-54-cd315" type="crimeDate">4th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-54-off314 t18080217-54-cd315"></join>, four pound weight of feathers, value 4 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18080217-54-victim505" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Dixon
                  <interp inst="t18080217-54-victim505" type="surname" value="Dixon"></interp>
